[3.5 Set Operations]
    - union (∪)
    - intersect (∩)
    - except (−)

    (3.5.1 The Union Operation)
        - union operation
            -> automatically eliminates duplicates!

        - "union all"
            -> retain all duplicates

    (3.5.2 The intersect Operation)
        - intersect operation
            -> automatically eliminates duplicates!

        - "intersect all"
            -> retains all duplicates

    (3.5.3 The Except Operation)
        - except operation
            -> outputs all tuples from its first input that do not occur in the second input
            -> automatically eliminates duplicates!

        - "except all"
            -> retains all duplicates
